snippet.title: Felvidek Trailer
snippet.description:
In Felvidek, a JRPG set in 15th century Slovakia, you embrace the role of an alcoholic knight Pavol. Meet diverse and interesting characters to help you drive out the Hussites and Ottomans who blight this land.

get on steam: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2299900/Felvidek/
story and dialogues written by Vlado Ganaj
music done by the amazing @marcelgidotesholycrab 

follow for more info: 
https://x.com/brozef_
https://x.com/vladoganaj
